{"tid":1470532,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要塞死機場 搞死香港 不服來辯","createTime":"2019-08-14T05:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T15:54:35.000Z","uid":76078,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75c9817175de4e3ab4bc77fb1e05ea3621085b38","tid":1470532,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:44:19.000Z","msg":"問：阻塞機場搞死香港？<br />\n答：「做法不完美，但可接受，可以再改善。」(高級警司李桂華, 2019-08-13)<br />\n<br />\n問：點解阻止公安離開？<br />\n答：「佢唔喺現場出現就冇事，去得果度就可能有呢啲風險」(保安局局長李家超, 2019-08-13)<br />\n<br />\n問：阻止救護帶佢離開？人命嚟㗎。<br />\n答：「而家眾說紛云，我認為事主可以去報警先，警方必定會跟進調查。」(高級警司李桂華, 2019-08-13)<br />\n<br />\n問：點解你地咁冇人性，濫用暴力，究竟想點？<br />\n「在場嘅市民只係用最低武力，當一切平靜後，真誠對話就會展開。」(香港特首林鄭月娥, 2019-08-13)<br />\n<br />\n問：如果遊客因此受傷，嚇怕外國人點算？<br />\n「咁我祝佢早日康復。」(香港特首林鄭月娥, 2019-08-13)"},{"pid":"ec69e1cfc0b7658d32f2e4afade27a8371b8ada0","tid":1470532,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"dee23dd86c0b4951a926e933c22b404a16ac8d9a","tid":1470532,"uid":29899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:49:39.000Z","msg":"統一機場戰線，大家點睇？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469174</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【公投】大家覺得如果我號召班基督徒嚟機場攞住文宣圖sing hallelujah 有冇得諗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470110\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470110</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[基督徒入] 求求你地入機場Sing Hallelujah<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469121</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c948baf0e853de8662e4c4bc8f0e28198c14471b","tid":1470532,"uid":279779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass